   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Support HOPE&apos;s Mothers&apos; Clubs in Bangladesh</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Mothers are crucial in promoting health within their families and for educating others. HOPE therefore established HOPE Mother&apos;s Clubs to do just that; ensure the spread of health education and prosperity of their families in the community. HOPE has established 38 Mother&apos;s Clubs in varying rural regions The Clubs meet once a month, and discuss the vital subjects such as: Diarrhea, Malaria, HIV/AIDS, Acute Respiratory Infection, Immunization, Nutrition, Family Planning, Safe Delivery, and more.</narrative>
  </description>
